<br>
speed buff drops weapon speed essentially<br>
<br>
well base damage is weapon speed * DPS  (not exactly but you guys get my drift)<br>
<br>
so damage per hit goes dows<br>
<br>
sounds like it sux, but then i thought about it<br>
<br>
my damage per hit is going down, but i'm hitting more often<br>
<br>
as long as i'm hitting more often (increase in percentage) is higher than my damage per hit is droping (again percentage) then we come out on top<br>
<br>
i think we kinda (all classes i belive) get screwed on styles cuz they are out &quot;one hit wonders&quot; and i don't belive they lower endurance hits with the speed buff<br>
<br>
speed buff is great for regular melee, seems to take a bit away from styles, tho we do preform them faster<br>
